# Write Artifacts to Disk

Every important output you produce must be written to the project tree. Do not leave plans, analysis, specs, or reports only in the conversation — they will be lost.

## Where Artifacts Go

| What you produced | Write it to |
| :--- | :--- |
| Execution plan for complex work | `docs/plans/active/{name}.md` |
| New or updated system spec | `specs/{system}.md` (and update `specs/README.md` index) |
| Analysis or audit report | `docs/reports/{name}.md` |
| Architecture decision | `docs/architecture.md` or the relevant spec |
| Quality assessment | `docs/quality.md` |
| New workflow | `.agents/workflows/{name}.md` |
